tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All parameters are within normal limits except for a mildly elevated HbA1c (6.4%), indicating impaired glucose metabolism or possible prediabetes/early diabetes. Renal function and electrolytes are normal. Recommend clinical correlation and consideration of lifestyle modification or further evaluation for glycemic control.
